Class TagStore

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.graph.specifications.common.element.store.TagStore
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.esotericsoftware.kryo.KryoSerializable, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.lifecycle.Initializable, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.Nameable, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.NamedObject
public class TagStore extends Object implements com.esotericsoftware.kryo.KryoSerializable, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.NamedObject, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.lifecycle.Initializable
Stores and retrieves tag lists for graph elements. The store can be constructed with TagStore(String, PbfTagCodec), passing in the tag codec used to compress and decompress tag lists. The method set(GraphElement, PbfTagList) stores a tag list for the given graph element and the method tagList(GraphElement) retrieves it again. The number of tag lists can be retrieved with size().
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
